                  </hi>. I live at Collet-place, Commercial-road About there o'clock in the afternoon of the 3rd of October, I was in Aldgate—I felt something about my coat-flap—I put my had down and felt a hand in contact with it—I turned, and saw the prisoner in the act of throwing my handkerchief away—I took him, and held till I saw a policeman—this is my handkerchief—I saw it leave his hand.</p>
